name: FVect
typ: (capacity : Nat) -> Fin (S capacity) -> Type -> Type

name: Nil
typ: FVect capacity FZ elem
elem -> FVect capacity len elem -> FVect (S capacity) (FS len) elem

name: consWeaker
typ: elem -> FVect (S n) (weaken len') elem -> FVect (S n) (FS len') elem

name: strengthenLT
typ: (j : Fin (S n)) -> {auto 0 _ : LT (finToNat j) n} -> Fin n

name: consLT
typ: {auto 0 ltPrf : LT (finToNat len) (S n)} -> elem -> FVect (S n) len elem -> FVect (S n) (FS (strengthenLT len)) elem
{auto 0 ltPrf : LT (finToNat len) (S n)} -> elem -> FVect (S n) len elem -> FVect (S n) (FS (strengthenLT len)) elem

name: empty
typ: (capacity : Nat) -> FVect capacity FZ elem

name: replicate
typ: (l : Fin (S capacity)) -> elem -> FVect capacity l elem

name: addCapacity
typ: FVect c l a -> FVect (S c) (weaken l) a

name: addCapacityN
typ: (n : Nat) -> FVect capacity l a -> FVect (capacity + n) (weakenN n l) a

name: removeCapacity
typ: FVect (S n) (weaken len') a -> FVect n len' a

name: length
typ: FVect capacity l a -> Nat

name: fromVect
typ: Vect l a -> FVect l last a

name: toVect
typ: FVect c l elem -> Vect (finToNat l) elem

name: tail
typ: FVect c (FS l) elem -> FVect c (weaken l) elem

name: dropFirst
typ: FVect (S c) (FS l) elem -> FVect c l elem

name: head
typ: FVect c (FS l) elem -> elem

name: last
typ: FVect c (FS l) elem -> elem

name: init
typ: FVect c (FS l) elem -> FVect c (weaken l) elem

name: dropLast
typ: FVect (S c) (FS l) elem -> FVect c l elem

name: fVectInjective
typ: x :: xs = y :: ys -> (x = y, xs = ys)

name: addRemoveCapacityInverse
typ: (xs : FVect c l elem) -> removeCapacity (addCapacity xs) = xs

name: lengthReifies
typ: (v : FVect c l elem) -> length v = finToNat l

name: catMaybes
typ: FVect capacity len (Maybe elem) -> (len' : Fin (S capacity) ** FVect capacity len' elem)

name: mapMaybes
typ: (elem -> Maybe elem') -> FVect capacity len elem -> (len' : Fin (S capacity) ** FVect capacity len' elem')

name: filter
typ: (elem -> Bool) -> FVect capacity len elem -> (len' : Fin (S capacity) ** FVect capacity len' elem)

name: Capacity
typ: Type -> Type

name: Full
typ: (0 _ : finToNat l = c) -> Capacity (FVect c l e)

name: NotFull
typ: (0 _ : LT (finToNat len) (S n)) -> Capacity (FVect (S n) len e)

name: capacity
typ: (0 _ : FVect c l e) -> Capacity (FVect c l e)

name: capacity'
typ: FVect c l e -> Capacity (FVect c l e)
